OL,3,CFuneral appeal for boy, 4, hit by bus
OL,4,Coutside hospital raises #6,000
OL,6,FA fundraising appeal for the funeral
OL,7,Fof a four-year-old boy who was hit by
OL,8,Fa bus has raised more than #6,000.
OL,10,FZaahir Jan died outside the Queen
OL,11,FElizabeth The Queen Mother Hospital in
OL,12,FMargate on Thursday 7 August, 2025.
OL,14,FHis mother Azaria Green has set up a
OL,15,FGoFundMe to help with the costs of her
OL,16,Fson's funeral.
