OL,3,CFuneral appeal for boy, 4, hit by bus
OL,4,Coutside hospital raises #6,000
OL,6,FZaahir was leaving the hospital after
OL,7,Fvisiting his grandmother when he was
OL,8,Fhit by a white single-decker
OL,9,FStagecoach bus near the entrance to
OL,10,Fthe A&E department.
OL,12,FAfter being struck by the bus, Zaahir
OL,13,Fwas taken back inside the hospital
OL,14,Fwhere he was pronounced dead soon
OL,15,Fafter.
OL,17,FOn Friday, his mother and other family
OL,18,Fmembers arrived outside the hospital
OL,19,Fclose to where Zaahir died.
