OL,6,FThey laid blankets, flowers and sweets
OL,7,Fin tribute, as well as writing letters
OL,8,Fto him.
OL,10,FHis father, Navid Feizi, said his son
OL,11,Fwas a "sweet and charming boy" and
OL,12,Fadded: "Even when he was hurt, he was
OL,13,Falways smiling."
OL,15,FOn the GoFundMe page, his mother
OL,16,Fwrote: "Everyone is devastated but
OL,17,Fthat word doesn't feel like enough to
OL,18,Fexplain how we are all feeling.
