OL,6,F"Our sweet funny boy with a cheeky
OL,7,Fsmile that could make anyone's heart
OL,8,Ffull.
OL,10,F" The smile that we can't see again.
OL,12,F"Can't hold him. Can't cuddle him.
OL,13,FCan't hear him. Can't have him
OL,14,Fsleeping in my bed tonight.
OL,16,F"But I can try to give him the best
OL,17,Fand most comfortable burial.
OL,19,F"My baby I wish you were in my bed
OL,20,Ftonight cuddling. I love you my boy".
