OL,6,FA spokesperson from Stagecoach said:
OL,7,F"We can confirm that one of our buses
OL,8,Fwas involved in a tragic incident
OL,9,Fwithin the grounds of Queen Elizabeth
OL,10,FThe Queen Mother Hospital in Margate.
OL,12,F"Emergency services attended the
OL,13,Fscene, and a child was taken into the
OL,14,Fhospital, where they sadly passed away.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts and deepest condolences
OL,17,Fare with the family and all those
OL,18,Faffected at this incredibly difficult
OL,19,Ftime.
